text: Kartlazma () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dmitriyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 34 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Zilair, 7 km from Dmitriyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Kartlazma
